item.title: d3 Methods as Data in ClojureScript
item.description: In the debut of my blog, I'd like to highlight the methods I've been learning through studying functional program design patterns. This post specifically shows the influence of Clojure's "it's all data" methodology while also giving some insight into the power of the language in the browser.
